original: Hultqvist, Sven Axelsson, komminister, Mariannelund, f. 28/10/09 i Lund av kyrkoh. Axel H. o. Elisabeth Sjöstedt. G. 38 m. Birgit Wingren. Barn: Astrid f. 40, Ingrid 43, Gunilla 46. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 28, teol. fil. ex. 29, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Linköp. stift 35. Tjg. s. past:adj. i Atvid, Hannäs, Vimmer-by o. Norrköp. samt s. v. kommin. i Hässileiby, kioimmin. där sed. 45, pr ed. å Hässleby san.,, timlär v. Mariannelunds prakt. sk. Skr.: iutg. Häsisileby förs. (årskrön. 43\ 47).
translated: Hultqvist, Sven Axelsson, vicar, Mariannelund, born on October 28, 1909 in Lund to vicar Axel H. and Elisabeth Sjöstedt. Married in 1938 to Birgit Wingren. Children: Astrid b. 1940, Ingrid b. 1943, Gunilla b. 1946. He completed high school in Stockholm in 1928, theology degree in 1929, practical theology exam and ordained priest of the Linköping diocese in 1935. He worked as assistant pastor in Atvid, Hannäs, Vimmerby and Norrköping, and as deputy pastor and then vicar in Hässleby from 1945. He was also a teacher at the practical school in Mariannelund. He authored publications for the Hassleby parish (yearbook 1943, 1947).
